data.text:
Top Dutch players in FIFA 22. The top players in FIFA 22 with Dutch nationality (Holland) which you can use in FUT to form a team with the maximum chemistry rate.

This list includes the top 30 Dutch players, top 10 Dutch attackers, top 10 Dutch midfielders, top 10 Dutch defenders and top 10 Dutch goalkeepers.
